<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAWIPA NANGMAH KAN DAWT DEUH CH74</title>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vawlei chawhlawn vialte nakin, Nangmah kha kan dawt deuh, A rawk kho
 lomi hnangamnak, Na ka zaangfah caah.

[C1]
   Dawtnak le velngeihnak bia kha (nak via kha) A cheu hmanh kan thei
   lo, Thiannak kong kha kan chim ahcun, A cheu hmanh kan thei lo.

[V2]
 Vawlei kawidua vialte nakin, Nangmah kha kan dawt deuh, Nangmah lawng
 kha hla tha nakin, A zungzal kan ruah deuh.

[C2]
   Dawtnak le velngeihnak bia kha (nak via kha) A cheu hmanh kan thei
   lo, Thiannak kong kha kan chim ahcun, A cheu hmanh kan thei lo.

[V3]
 Ka lung kha na ka lawmhter cang, Hi ca zungzal kaa lawm, Dawtnak kha a
 um lo ahcun, Lungrawhnak a um lai.

[C3]
   Dawtnak le velngeihnak bia kha (nak via kha) A cheu hmanh kan thei
   lo, Thiannak kong kha kan chim ahcun, A cheu hmanh kan thei lo.

[V4]
 Maw a sung bik ka Khamhtu Bawi, Nang he kan um ahcun; Vawlei cung
 khuazei ka hmanh ah, Zeitluk in kan i lawm!

[C4]
   Dawtnak le velngeihnak bia kha (nak via kha) A cheu hmanh kan thei
   lo, Thiannak kong kha kan chim ahcun, A cheu hmanh kan thei lo.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>74</hymn_number>
</song>